hot ir gezogt aza geboy halb in der erd un halb in der heykh. zemlyanke, UNK.

00:22:48.203 --> 00:22:51.386
ya, halb in der heykh. zey hobn dos ongerufn zemlyankes.

00:22:52.506 --> 00:22:56.360
in di zemlyankes iz geven nares, un m'hot farteylt

00:22:56.360 --> 00:22:59.773
yedern in zayn barak, yedern zayn nomen farshribn.

