ikh bin arayngefaln, zaynen mir ayngefaln fir

00:24:07.070 --> 00:24:12.791
y- yunglekhe kinder, s'iz gekumen der fun kikh, er hot gezen az mir zaynen yunglekhe, hor er undz genumen arbetn in kikh.

00:24:13.253 --> 00:24:14.970
di kikh, a daytshishe kikh

00:24:14.970 --> 00:24:16.880
vos zi fleg kokhn far di postns.

00:24:17.083 --> 00:24:20.874
dos hot ⟨men nit⟩ gedarft aroyfgeyn mer nit oyfn bergl. dos iz geven oysern lager

00:24:21.572 --> 00:24:26.797
un me fleg darfn helfn. trogn bulves, aroystrogn di mist o-, in kikh flegt er undz nit araynlozn.

00:24:27.006 --> 00:24:28.639
in kikh fleg men nit kenen arayngeyn.

00:24:28.639 --> 00:24:30.300
ober lebn kikh hobn mir gearbet.

