hobn zikh shoyn ⟨PAYAVet⟩ nokh etlekhe kinder far vo- "ah, zey arbetn in kikh. me ken dortn esn

00:24:53.078 --> 00:24:57.493
vayl esn hot men glaykh gegebn veynik. in lager hot men gegebn zeyer veynik esn.

00:24:57.634 --> 00:25:00.631
dernokh vel ikh dertseyln vayter vos iz gevorn mitn esn.

00:25:02.190 --> 00:25:07.280
oyfn firtn tog zaynen shoyn geven bay, bay, bay fuftsn kinder. ale viln geyn arbetn.

00:25:07.388 --> 00:25:10.101
er nemt mer nit vi tsen, finf. er nemt!

00:25:10.101 --> 00:25:12.731
ikh bin dokh laykht, nemt tsu der arbet.

00:25:13.682 --> 00:25:18.198
beys s'iz gekumen der, NACHALNIK, dos heyst,

00:25:18.998 --> 00:25:20.359
der glavner kapo

00:25:20.432 --> 00:25:21.669
der glavner

00:25:21.669 --> 00:25:22.805
lager firer

