fun finf bukves hot men gedarft ⟨zogn⟩ ve-

00:26:48.927 --> 00:26:51.484
fun finf, fir, finf tsifern hob ikh gezogt dem nomer.

00:26:53.312 --> 00:26:56.579
un m'hot undz avekgefirt bay der arbet. oyf morgn in der fri

00:26:56.653 --> 00:26:58.173
beys s'iz geven der apel

00:26:58.173 --> 00:27:03.683
