khuts dem hobn tsunoyfgeklibn nokh a sakh kinder

00:27:11.250 --> 00:27:13.842
s'hot zikh tsunoyfgeklibn iber hundert

00:27:14.558 --> 00:27:17.015
kinder, ober mi- ikh bin nit geven in di

00:27:17.798 --> 00:27:18.551
⟨ikh bin⟩

