veys ikh UNK gezogt, ober keyner iz nit dervayle nokh ⟨nit⟩ gekumen. keyner lebt nit.

00:27:34.335 --> 00:27:37.327
m'hot gezogt ⟨vos⟩ UNK firt zey UNK AUSCHWITZ, me firt zey

00:27:37.327 --> 00:27:40.356
nor vayzt oys hot men zey avekgefirt in DACHAU, un dortn hot men zey

00:27:40.356 --> 00:27:41.231
farbrent.

